WHEREAS, Lana Grace Overton plans to attend Louisiana State University in the
fall to study biology, with the goal of pursuing a career in veterinary medicine, a path that
aligns with her academic strengths and demonstrated commitment to animal care and
community service; and
WHEREAS, Lana Grace Overton's achievements bring great pride to Denham
Springs High School, Livingston Parish Public Schools, and the state of Louisiana, and serve
as an inspiration to her peers and community.
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana
does hereby commend and congratulate Lana Grace Overton on being selected as the 2025-
2026 "Student of the Year" at Denham Springs High School in Livingston Parish.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that a copy of this Resolution be transmitted to Lana
Grace Overton.
PRESIDENT OF THE SENATE
